oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ox cart
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Slide film (or reversal film) of an oxen pulling a cart. Kinsall took this photograph while he was stationed at the Osan Air Base in South Korea.

Kinsall was stationed from July 1954 - December 1954 at the Osan Air Base, an United States Air Force base, which is located in the city of Pyeongtaek, South Korea. While stationed in Osan Air Base, Kinsall was a Director of Base Personnel.
